        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>SIP_SVC_PROTO_CMD_SYNC<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Typical flow, synchronous request. Service expects EL3/EL2 firmware to return the result immediately during SMC/HVC call.</para>
