<para>SIP_SVC_PROTO_CMD_ASYNC<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Asynchronous request. Service is required to poll the response via a separate SMC/HVC call. Use this method if the request requires longer processing in EL3/EL2. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
