</para>
<para>SIP_SVC_PROTO_STATUS_UNKNOWN<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Unrecognized SMC/HVC Function ID.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>SIP_SVC_PROTO_STATUS_BUSY<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The request is still in progress. Please try again.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>SIP_SVC_PROTO_STATUS_REJECT<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The request have been rejected due to improper input data.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
