    <briefdescription>
<para>Arm SiP services communication protocol between service provider and client. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Client to fill in the input data in struct <ref refid="structsip__svc__request" kindref="compound">sip_svc_request</ref> format when requesting SMC/HVC service via &apos;send&apos; function.</para>
<para>Service to fill in the SMC/HVC return value in struct <ref refid="structsip__svc__response" kindref="compound">sip_svc_response</ref> format and pass to client via Callback. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
